title: Day D Time Mayhem Level Fix + 1 Cheat [The War Criminal/SGR]
description:
Day D Time Mayhem Level 16 Fix +1 Trainer by The War Criminal / SGR

1- Install the game if you have not already
2- Install Dot Net Framework 4.5 Full Setup if it is not on your system (fix requires it)
3- Click on fix file to fix game and use the trainer/cheat.


If you already have the game installed, skip downloading the game (daydtimemayhem2013.exe).

If you already have Dot Net Framework 4.5 installed skip downloading it (dotnetfx45_full_setup.exe)

Game fix files are:
daydtimemayhemfix-sgr.exe
sgr.dat

You can run the fix without downloading the sgr.dat file. If you do, there will be no music.
